data.name: txt_Three.Text
data.value:
After placing the desired bet amount. Hit the "Roll" button to start playing. After rolling the dice you can either win, lose or gain a point. If a point is gained the rest of the bets will be unlocked (Hardways, Big 6 & Big 8).
The point will appear on the screen right above the numbers, just like shown in the picture.
Now, you can simply choose the desired betting amount and select where you want to bet. But pay close attention because every bet has different pay rate. Big 6 and Big 8 as well as the Pass Line and Don't Pass Line bets will only grant you the placed betting amount times 2. Whereas, the hardways will pay from times 8 to times 31 your betting amount.
